					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/11/business/media/11scooter.html?ex=1339214400&amp;en=c55201bd7d37e2d7&amp;ei=5088&amp;partner=rssnyt&amp;emc=rss&quot;&gt;NY Times&lt;/a&gt;: &quot;The lawyers for I. Lewis Libby Jr. last month invoked the rarely used courtroom tactic: the 'bloggers can be mean' defense.&quot;" created="Tue, 12 Jun 2007 01:28:24 GMT"/>
